always be thick,

50:51.916 --> 50:53.215
never foamy,

50:53.217 --> 50:58.454
and always
go on light,

50:58.456 --> 51:02.124
never heavy.

51:03.160 --> 51:06.128
You sure you want
to get into this?

51:09.299 --> 51:11.500
I'm here, aren't I?

51:11.502 --> 51:13.335
Yeah. Yeah.

51:13.337 --> 51:14.703
All right.

51:17.808 --> 51:19.742
There was, uh...

51:19.744 --> 51:22.111
There was
this detective once

51:22.113 --> 51:24.213
who got it
in his head

51:24.215 --> 51:25.748
I was the guy
for a case

51:25.750 --> 51:26.816
he was working.

51:26.818 --> 51:27.818
Mm.

51:27.819 --> 51:28.819
Couldn't let it go.

51:28.820 --> 51:30.252
Head back.

51:32.322 --> 51:34.090
So one day,

51:34.092 --> 51:37.059
he shows up
out of nowhere,

51:37.061 --> 51:38.360
hauls me in,

51:38.362 --> 51:41.030
and starts grilling me
about some phone calls.

51:41.032 --> 51:42.965
Apparently
this detective had

51:42.967 --> 51:44.266
been getting calls

51:44.268 --> 51:47.536
from some... heh...
phantom caller

51:47.538 --> 51:51.006
claiming he'd
abducted a woman,

51:51.008 --> 51:53.042
buried her alive.

51:53.044 --> 51:55.311
Relax your face.

51:55.313 --> 51:57.246
So he showed me
the transcripts

51:57.248 --> 51:58.848
of these calls, right,

51:58.850 --> 52:01.684
see how
I'd react to 'em.

52:01.686 --> 52:04.687
And this guy
would say things like,

52:04.689 --> 52:06.255
"I took
another one, Tom,

52:06.257 --> 52:08.924
"told her not to panic.

52:08.926 --> 52:12.128
"If she stays calm,

52:12.130 --> 52:14.263
you have
at least two hours."

52:14.265 --> 52:16.432
Every time
another girl

52:16.434 --> 52:17.466
went missing,

52:17.468 --> 52:20.202
he'd get another call
and just...

52:21.271 --> 52:22.771
go into this frenzy,

52:22.773 --> 52:24.773
trying to piece
together clues

52:24.775 --> 52:26.242
before it was
too late.

52:26.244 --> 52:30.779
This guy would ask him,
"Is that enough time?

52:30.781 --> 52:32.715
You have
all the time you need."

52:32.717 --> 52:36.118
I never seen
anyone so angry.

52:36.120 --> 52:37.920
And there
was this one thing

52:37.922 --> 52:39.155
I'll never forget.

52:39.157 --> 52:42.858
He says, "You lost
another one, Tom.

52:42.860 --> 52:45.027
"You never
could figure out

52:45.029 --> 52:48.497
"how to put your ear
to the ground and

52:48.499 --> 52:49.832
really listen.

52:49.834 --> 52:53.102
And the girls,
they never really

52:53.104 --> 52:55.271
could stay calm."

52:56.673 --> 53:04.180
I guess they went
back and forth like that

53:04.182 --> 53:07.283
until this cop
couldn't take it anymore.

53:07.285 --> 53:10.052
He knew there was
something odd about me,

53:10.054 --> 53:12.121
and I told him I didn't
know anything about

53:12.123 --> 53:13.355
