53:40.051 --> 53:44.220
start over fresh.

53:44.222 --> 53:45.955
Out with the old...

53:47.924 --> 53:49.858
and in with the new.

53:49.860 --> 53:51.227
Would you
look at that?

53:51.229 --> 53:55.297
There's a handsome young man
under there.

53:58.435 --> 54:02.972
